Infographic: Travelling to work turns increasingly painful 
5-3-2017 
Travelling to work turns increasingly painful

A study by MoveInSync, a transportation startup, reveals that employees commuting to workplaces in Gurugram take the longest time and cover the longest distance to reach their workplaces of all cities in India. Here is a look at the average time people take to commute to their workplaces in different parts of the country. 
